 <p>
  <br/>
  <span style="font-weight: 400">
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    ADDICTED / hooked
    <br/>
    Note: I'm not sticking my finger in my mouth.  I'm just pressing the tip of 
an "X" handshape into my cheek near the corner of my mouth. Then I pull my head 
to the side as if representing a fish that has been "hooked."
